  "remarks": "CFe.002 Emerged in northern Uganda in the 1980s. Has engaged in the abduction, killing and mutilation of thousands of civilians in Central Africa, including hundreds in the Central African Republic. The leader is Joseph Kony (CFi.009).; Listing: Listed on: 7 Mar. 2016",
